title: 50 The Warrior Going Forward
description:
In today's episode, we'll attempt to bring all the threads of this series together -- Spartans and Athenians, Alexander the Great, Arjuna and Krishna, the concept of the Inner War, and evolution of the Archetypes. Don't worry, there will be more episodes going forward, in which we'll dig even more deeply into this amazing and fascinating subject. Thanks for sticking with us!

New episodes every Monday. SUBSCRIBE and REVIEW.
